This github repository contains:
- HockeyEDA 
  - Notebook for our exploratory data analysis as well as our power ranking. This notebook also creates a few initial aggregated tables with feature engineering variables that we use in later notebooks. 
- hockeyModelMAIN
  - Notebook for our main 1st round prediction hockey model. 
- Offense1v2Disp
  - Notebook for our creating offensive team disparity.  
- HockeyVisualizations
  - Notebook for visualizing the correlation between power ranking and offensive team disparity. 
